Why haven't you submitted an article to Zaph? I know I have been badgering everyone about contributing something but the above post would make an excellent front page headline. I strongly believe that if humanity doesn't take space soon it may lose the opportunity. Call me a pessimist but I sincerely believe it. There are too many ways in which our precarious hold on spaceflight might be lost. Possibly forever if an Asteroid hits before we are ready. Asteroids may be one of the more violent ways in which we might fall from grace and not the most likely but it could very well wipe us clean off the face of this Planet.  <p>
